     F********************************************* ECQR15 **
     FECSPW20 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     F                                        RRN1  KSFILE SFL01
     F                                              KINFDS @INFDS
     FECSPL10 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FECSPL20 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FGCQPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#PPCT IF  E           K        DISK
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
     E                    CMD     1   3 78
     E                    MSG     1   3 78
